ing: 1 (3.9 ounce) package instant chocolate pudding mix
1 (8 ounce) container frozen whipped topping, thawed
1 (9 inch) prepared chocolate cookie crumb crust
des: "A chocolate chocolate experience that's creamy and delicious.  To cut this pie easily, use knife dipped in water."
ins:
Prepare pudding as directed for pie filling; let set.
When pudding is set, fold in whipped topping and crushed cookies.  Pour pudding mixture into crust.
Freeze overnight.  Serve.
